---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research Portfolio - AI & Explainable Machine Learning" description="Explore my research in deep learning, explainable AI, and sentiment analysis for mental health applications at Xi'an Jiaotong University">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-teal-50 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Research <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-teal-600">Portfolio</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Advancing artificial intelligence research with a focus on explainability, interpretability,
          and real-world applications for mental health and social impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">2+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-700">Years of Research</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-2">3</div>
          <div class="text-gray-700">Active Projects</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">1</div>
          <div class="text-gray-700">Conference Presentations</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Current Research -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Current Research</h2>
        <!-- <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Active projects at Xi'an Jiaotong University</p> -->
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Research Project 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="md:w-1/3 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-800">AI4Health</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3 p-8">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">EASRL-MH: Enhanced Adaptive Symptom Reasoning Learning for Mental Health.</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium">Xi'an Jiaotong University | 2023 - Present</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">

                Research mainly focused on AI for healthcare, especially for mental health. 
                <br>
                Developed <strong>EASRL-MH: Enhanced Adaptive Symptom Reasoning Learning for Mental Health.</strong>
                This is a project intended to assist mental health diagnosis through reinforcement learning. <br>
                Through selecting the most informative questions to ask, the model can diagnose the patient's mental disorder with high accuracy and relatively low number of questions.
                Our model has achieved state-of-the-art results on the <a href="https://www.hcp.med.harvard.edu/ncs/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-600 underline hover:no-underline">NCS-R benchmark dataset</a>, 
                successfully shortening the length of interview to an <strong>average of 9.6 questions with 86.4% accuracy and an AUC-ROC of 0.92</strong>.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Key Contributions:</h4>
                  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>Reinforcement learning for mental health diagnosis</li>
                    <li>State-of-the-art results on the NCS-R benchmark dataset</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">AI4Health</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">Reinforcement Learning</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">Mental Health</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Research Project 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="md:w-1/3 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-100 to-teal-200 p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-teal-600 mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-800">Explainable AI (XAI)</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3 p-8">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">A BERT-Based Emotion Diagnosis Support System with Improved Explainability</h3>
                <p class="text-teal-600 font-medium">Northwestern Polytechnical University,on behalf of China Talented Youth Project | 2024 - 2025</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                Developed an <strong>AI emotional classification system based on BERT</strong>. 
                The key innovation is the application of <strong>Local Interpretable Model-Agnostic Explanations (LIME)</strong> to improve the explainability of the model.
                The model achieved <strong>over 95% classification accuracy</strong> on the Sentiment140 dataset consisting over 160 million tweets. 
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Research Focus:</h4>
                  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>BERT-based emotion classification</li>
                    <li>LIME for explainability</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-sm rounded-full">BERT</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-sm rounded-full">LIME</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-sm rounded-full">Explainable AI (XAI)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Research Project 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="md:w-1/3 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-teal-100 p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-800">Educational AI</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3 p-8">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI-Powered Educational Tools</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium">Personal Research Project | 2024 - Present</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                Investigating how AI can enhance computer science education, particularly for younger learners.
                This research combines insights from my teaching experience with COMPSCI 0.10 to develop
                intelligent tutoring systems and adaptive learning platforms.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Innovation Areas:</h4>
                  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>Adaptive assessment systems that adjust to student learning pace</li>
                    <li>AI-powered code review and feedback for beginner programmers</li>
                    <li>Natural language interfaces for programming education</li>
                    <li>Gamification strategies enhanced by machine learning</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">Educational Technology</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">Adaptive Learning</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">Code Analysis</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-sm rounded-full">Gamification</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Research Philosophy -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Research Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">How I approach problems and create meaningful impact</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Impact-Driven Research</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Every research project I undertake starts with a real-world problem. I believe the most meaningful
            AI research is that which can directly improve people's lives, whether through better healthcare,
            more accessible education, or more interpretable systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-teal-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Explainability First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            As AI systems become more powerful, making them interpretable becomes more crucial. I prioritize
            developing methods that not only perform well but can also explain their reasoning to users,
            especially in high-stakes applications.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Interdisciplinary Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The best AI research happens at the intersection of computer science with other fields. My work
            actively seeks collaboration with educators, psychologists, and domain experts to ensure
            technical solutions meet real human needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-teal-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ethical AI Development</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Responsible AI development requires considering privacy, fairness, and societal impact from the
            beginning. I integrate ethical considerations into every stage of research, from data collection
            to model deployment and evaluation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Publications and Presentations -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Publications & Presentations</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Sharing research findings with the academic community</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-l-4 border-primary-500">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                Explainable AI Approaches for Student Mental Health Assessment
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
                Presented at the China Talented Youth Program National Conference, 2024
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                Research presentation to leading university professors on applying explainable AI techniques
                to mental health applications in educational settings.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 ml-4">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-primary-100 text-primary-800">
                Conference
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-l-4 border-teal-500">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                Democratizing CS Education: A Case Study in Elementary School Programming
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
                In preparation for Educational Technology Conference, 2024
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                Analysis of COMPSCI 0.10 curriculum effectiveness and methodologies for teaching computer science
                concepts to young learners.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 ml-4">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-teal-100 text-teal-800">
                In Progress
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Future Research Directions -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-teal-600 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Future Research Directions</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8">
        Looking ahead to the next frontiers in AI research and education
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Multimodal AI for Education</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-100">
            Combining vision, language, and behavioral data to create more comprehensive educational AI systems
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Cross-Cultural AI Ethics</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-100">
            Developing AI systems that respect and adapt to different cultural contexts and values
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-primary-600 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Collaborate With Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>